calAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"• PII masking em logs mas NÃO em prompts — Gemini recebe CPFs reais\n• Sem consentimento granular (violação LGPD Art. 7)\n• Sem DSR. Sem LGPD cleanup automático","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},{"id":"p6_s9_bg","type":"rectangle","x":50,"y":11131,"width":2600,"height":30,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#e0f2f1","backgroundColor":"#e0f2f1","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":526899916,"version":1,"versionNonce":330813823,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"locked":false},{"id":"p6_s9_title","type":"text","x":60,"y":11136,"width":2580,"height":22,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#00695c","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":905126481,"version":1,"versionNonce":250014406,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"9. RESILIÊNCIA, FALLBACK DE LLM & PROVIDERS (Seções 13, 16)","fontSize":16,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"9. RESILIÊNCIA, FALLBACK DE LLM & PROVIDERS (Seções 13, 16)","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},{"id":"p6_s9_narrative","type":"text","x":60,"y":11171,"width":2580,"height":76,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#334155","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":493266761,"version":1,"versionNonce":310114427,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"POR QUE IMPORTA: Se o LLM cai, o sistema inteiro para. A LIA resolve com cascade multi-provider (Claude→Gemini→GPT-4o) —\npraticamente nenhuma plataforma de HR Tech documenta isso. São 25+ circuit breakers com SLOs formais (Netflix Hystrix pattern).\nO v5 depende 100% de Gemini — vendor lock-in total. Se Google mudar preço ou API, 100% do sistema é impactado.\nCircuit breaker do v5 é global e testado, mas sem cascade o circuito não tem para onde redirecionar.","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"POR QUE IMPORTA: Se o LLM cai, o sistema inteiro para. A LIA resolve com cascade multi-provider (Claude→Gemini→GPT-4o) —\npraticamente nenhuma plataforma de HR Tech documenta isso. São 25+ circuit breakers com SLOs formais (Netflix Hystrix pattern).\nO v5 depende 100% de Gemini — vendor lock-in total. Se Google mudar preço ou API, 100% do sistema é impactado.\nCircuit breaker do v5 é global e testado, mas sem cascade o circuito não tem para onde redirecionar.","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},{"id":"p6_s9_lia_pro_bg","type":"rectangle","x":50,"y":11257,"width":1250,"height":125,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#e2e8f0","backgroundColor":"#e8f5e9","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":985189230,"version":1,"versionNonce":496410667,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"locked":false},{"id":"p6_s9_v5_pro_bg","type":"rectangle","x":1400,"y":11257,"width":1250,"height":125,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#e2e8f0","backgroundColor":"#e3f2fd","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":543753716,"version":1,"versionNonce":573979305,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"locked":false},{"id":"p6_s9_lia_pro_title","type":"text","x":60,"y":11262,"width":1230,"height":20,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#2e7d32","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":31663831,"version":1,"versionNonce":872655217,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"✅ LIA","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"✅ LIA","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},{"id":"p6_s9_v5_pro_title","type":"text","x":1410,"y":11262,"width":1230,"height":20,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#0d47a1","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":125906158,"version":1,"versionNonce":117606778,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"✅ v5","fontSize":14,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"✅ v5","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},{"id":"p6_s9_lia_pro","type":"text","x":60,"y":11282,"width":1230,"height":95,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#334155","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":127952624,"version":1,"versionNonce":478293511,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"• 25+ circuit breakers por serviço com SLOs (threshold=5, window=60s)\n• LLM cascade Claude→Gemini→GPT-4o — resiliência máxima\n• DLQ (Dead Letter Queue) Redis LIST — nenhuma task falha silenciosamente\n• Degraded mode (Sprint F1-03) — respostas pré-programadas quando tudo falha\n• Factory pattern — adicionar novo provider é mudança isolada","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"• 25+ circuit breakers por serviço com SLOs (threshold=5, window=60s)\n• LLM cascade Claude→Gemini→GPT-4o — resiliência máxima\n• DLQ (Dead Letter Queue) Redis LIST — nenhuma task falha silenciosamente\n• Degraded mode (Sprint F1-03) — respostas pré-programadas quando tudo falha\n• Factory pattern — adicionar novo provider é mudança isolada","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},{"id":"p6_s9_v5_pro","type":"text","x":1410,"y":11282,"width":1230,"height":95,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#334155","backgroundColor":"transparent","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":null,"seed":115836548,"version":1,"versionNonce":733166281,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"locked":false,"text":"• Circuit breaker testado (unit + integration tests)\n• LangGraph RetryPolicy no autonomous — retry nativo\n• ModelRouter fast/default/heavy — otimização custo intra-Gemini\n• create_tracked_llm() integra tracking automaticamente\n• llm_cache_service.py (Redis) evita chamadas duplicadas","fontSize":13,"fontFamily":1,"textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"• Circuit breaker testado (unit + integration tests)\n• LangGraph RetryPolicy no autonomous — retry nativo\n• ModelRouter fast/default/heavy — otimização custo intra-Gemini\n• create_tracked_llm() integra tracking automaticamente\n• llm_cache_service.py (Redis) evita chamadas duplicadas","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},{"id":"p6_s9_lia_con_bg","type":"rectangle","x":50,"y":11392,"width":1250,"height":87,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#e2e8f0","backgroundColor":"#ffebee","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":763797677,"version":1,"versionNonce":2127492,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"locked":false},{"id":"p6_s9_v5_con_bg","type":"rectangle","x":1400,"y":11392,"width":1250,"height":87,"angle":0,"strokeColor":"#e2e8f0","backgroundColor":"#ffebee","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"groupIds":[],"roundness":{"type":3},"seed":781039482,"version":1,"versionNonce":331785108,"isDeleted":false,"boundElements":null,"updated":1774820222848,"link":null,"lock